txt.en: Wanted: Polished Sword Sheaths\n\nThe dwarves of the mining expedition have requested a collection of polished sword sheaths.
This collection box is checked daily by the dwarves. Your collection is sure to reach the requesting party.
The dwarves of the mining expedition have requested a collection of polished sword sheaths.
Collect polished sword sheaths and drop them in a collection box ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Collection boxes for this task can be found in the major hubs of Moria.\n\nYou should bring the trophies you gathered to a collection box.
